<?xml version="1.0" encoding="US-ASCII"?>
<document size="LETTER" margin-left="35" margin-right="35" margin-top="30" margin-bottom="30">

	<encryption allow-fillin="false" allow-modify-contents="false" allow-degraded-printing="true" allow-screen-readers="false" allow-copy="false"	allow-printing="false"/>
	<meta author="JIMS2, Harris County" creator="JIMS2, Harris County" title="Closing Letter"/>

	<module>
		<font-def name="title" family="Helvetica" style="bold" size="12"/>
		<font-def name="header" family="Helvetica" style="bold|underline" size="12"/>
		<font-def name="label" family="Helvetica" style="bold" size="11"/>
		<font-def name="text" family="Helvetica" style="normal" size="11"/>
		<font-def name="text-large" family="Helvetica" style="normal" size="12"/>
		<font-def name="text-small" family="Helvetica" style="normal" size="9"/>
		<font-def name="text-italic" family="Helvetica" style="bold|italic" size="11"/>
		<font-def name="letterheader" family="Helvetica" style="bold" size="12"/>
		
		<custom-tag alias="std-title" tag="paragraph">
			<attribute name="font" value="text-italic"/>
		</custom-tag>
		
		<custom-tag alias="letterheader" tag="paragraph">
			<attribute name="font" value="letterheader"/>
		</custom-tag>
	</module>

    <new-page size="LETTER" margin-left="35" margin-right="35" margin-top="30" margin-bottom="30">
    </new-page>
	
	<table columns="2" border-style="none" border-width="0" widths="15,85" padding="0" >
		<table-row halign="left">
	        <cell halign="left" valign="top" >
	            <paragraph>
	                <image source="MJCW/HarrisCountySeal.jpg" width="75" height="75" scale-to-fit="true"/>
	            </paragraph>
	        </cell>
	        <cell halign="left" valign="top">
	        	<table columns="2" padding="3" border-width="0" >
	        		<table-row>
				        <cell colspan = "2" halign="left" border-style="bottom" border-width="2" border-color="gray" padding-bottom="5">
							<letterheader>
								HARRIS COUNTY
							</letterheader> 	
							<letterheader>
								JUVENILE PROBATION DEPARTMENT
							</letterheader> 	
						</cell>
				    </table-row>	
    	        	<table-row>
    	        	   <cell halign="left" valign="top" >
						  _if_( ${locationUnitName} notEmpty )
						  	<paragraph font="text">
						  		<b>${locationUnitName}</b>
						  	</paragraph>
						  _endif_
						 _if_( ${locationAddress} isDefined)
						   	<paragraph font="text">
								${locationAddress.streetAddress}
							</paragraph>
							<paragraph font="text">									
								${locationAddress.cityStateZip}
						  	</paragraph>
						  _endif_
      				</cell>				
      				<cell halign="right" valign="top">
						<paragraph halign="right" font="text-small" align="top">
							<b>${managerFirstName} ${managerLastName}</b> 
						</paragraph>
						<paragraph halign="right" font="text-small" align="top">
							Caseload Manager
						</paragraph>
						<paragraph halign="right" font="text-small" align="top">	
							Office ${managerPhone}
						</paragraph>	
				    </cell>		  	
		 		  </table-row>
            	</table>    
	        </cell>
		</table-row>        
	</table>
	
	<paragraph font="text" spacing-after="20" spacing-before="50">    				
  		Date: <u>${currentDate}</u>
  	</paragraph>
  		
	<paragraph font="text">
  		${juvenile.fullNameFirst}
  	</paragraph>	
  	<paragraph font="text">	
		c/o ${guardianName.fullNameFirst}
	</paragraph>	
	<paragraph font="text">	
		${guardianAddress.streetAddress}
	</paragraph>	
	<paragraph font="text" spacing-after="20">	
   		${guardianAddress.cityStateZip}
  	</paragraph> 
  			
	<paragraph font="text" spacing-after="25">
		Supervision#: ${casefileId}
	</paragraph>
	
	<paragraph font="text" spacing-after="10">
		${juvenile.fullNameFirst}, this letter is to acknowledge that you have completed your period of probation
		supervision or Informal Adjustment assigned to you under supervision of the Harris County Juvenile
		Probation Department.  Your case file with Harris County Juvenile Probation is now closed.
	</paragraph>
	<paragraph font="text" spacing-after="10">
		Generally speaking your juvenile court records are confidential; however, this rule does not apply to 
		everyone or all situations.  The State of Texas has laws that appear within the Texas Family Code (i.e., 
		sections 58.003 and 58.208) that explain the confidentiality of juvenile court records and to whom it
		applies.  These sections of the Texas Family Code also provide the procedures for Sealing of Juvenile
		Court Records and Automatic Restricted Access.
	</paragraph>
	<paragraph font="text" spacing-after="10">
		The sealing of records is a procedure whereby you ask the Court to instruct anyone having records 
		relating to a juvenile's case to have them sent to the Court where they will be sealed.  Thereby, the 
		juvenile's Court records can only be made available for review by a Court order.  Automatic restricted
		access is a procedure in which the Texas Department of Public Safety will certify that a juvenile's case
		qualifies for restricted access.  Upon certification, persons or agencies in possession of a juvenile's court
		records may not disclose the existence of the court records to anyone not authorized by statue or law.
	</paragraph>
	<paragraph font="text" spacing-after="70">
		The laws regarding the sealing of records, and automatic restricted access are very specific so read the 
		attached material carefully.  If you have any further questions, please call your attorney.
	</paragraph>

   	<table columns="2" widths="60,40" keep-together="true">
		<table-row>
			<cell></cell>
			<cell>${officerFirstName} ${officerLastName}</cell>
		</table-row>
		<table-row>
			<cell></cell>
			<cell>Juvenile Probation Officer</cell>
		</table-row>
	</table>
    
</document>